:::{#def-stred}

#### Standardized residuals

$$r_i = \frac{e_i}{\widehat{SD}(e_i)}$$

:::

Hence, with enough data and a correct model, the standardized residuals will be approximately standard Gaussian; that is,

$$
r_i \siid N(0,1)
$$

